  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ukraine: help disabled children affected by war</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">As hundreds of thousands of Ukrainians escape to safety, many more are left behind. The most vulnerable have no options for escape. Disabled children are trapped as Russian troops invade. Days of sheltering as air raid sirens scream to stay indoors mean many families face food and essential supplies shortages. People who can go to stores wait in hours-long queues. For families with disabled children, the burden is intensified. Some already face starvation as supplies become scarce.</narrative>
  </description>
